articles.title: Australian social media ban on under-16s approved by parliament - BBC.com
articles.description: The ban aims to reduce "harms" on children and will take at least a year to implement, the PM says.
articles.content:
Australia will ban children under 16 from using social media, after its parliament approved the world's strictest laws.
